巴西1356名罪犯越狱，还劫持了狱警！疫情紧张，美国也开始释放部分囚犯。
1356 Brazilian criminals have escaped and jailed prison warders! The United States has begun releasing some prisoners in a tense situation.
中国经营报                      。
China Business News.
中国经营报。
China Business News.
与中国企业同步成长，对话商业领袖，传播商业理想，服务商业人群，《中国经营报》掌控中国商界绝对话语权。
Growing in step with Chinese companies, dialogue with business leaders, spreading business ideals, serving the business community, The China Business Administration controls the absolute voice of the Chinese business community.
。
.
据央视新闻援引巴西媒体报道，当地时间3月16日，巴西有3所监狱同时发生越狱事件，逃亡人数分别为400人、926人及30人，共计1356人。
Prison escapes broke out in Brazil on March 16 in three prisons, with 400 escapees (400), 926 (926) and 30 (1,356), the CCTV news quoted Brazilian media as saying.
据悉，受疫情影响，巴西监狱系统实行了新规，有监狱原定于次日（17日）进行的放风活动被取消，囚犯进行反抗并劫持了狱警等工作人员。
It is reported that the impact of the epidemic, the Brazilian prison system has introduced new regulations, some of the scheduled day (17) of the prison activities were cancelled, prisoners resisted and prison officers and other staff were abducted.
在防范疫情传播方面，监狱是个特殊的地方。
Prisons are a special place to guard against the spread of the epidemic.
在美国加利福尼亚州洛杉矶县，警局正在通过提前释放囚犯等方法减少监狱人口。
In Los Angeles County, California, the police are trying to reduce the prison population, including by releasing prisoners early.
巴西上千名罪犯越狱据巴西媒体报道，当地时间16日晚，在巴西圣保罗州一所监狱，约400名囚犯集体越狱。
About 400 inmates broke out of a prison in Sao Paulo, Brazil, on the night of Monday, Brazilian media reported.
据悉，囚犯因原定于次日（17日）进行的放风活动被取消而进行反抗，并劫持了狱警等工作人员。
It is reported that prisoners due to the next day (17) to carry out activities were cancelled resistance, and hijacked prison officers and other staff.
随后，囚犯集体逃脱，但逃脱路径及越狱的具体细节仍在调查中。
Subsequently, the prisoners escaped collectively, but the exact details of the escape route and escape are still under investigation.
Play目前，当地军警及民警等已动用直升机等展开全力搜查。
Play, the local military police and civilian police, and other helicopters have been used to conduct full search.
据报道，事发监狱是一所半开放式监狱，即囚犯可在白天自由参加生产改造活动，晚上返回囚室休息。
It was reported that the prison was a semi-open prison in which prisoners were free to participate in productive activities during the day and to return to their cells at night to rest.
该监狱最多可收押1640名囚犯。
The prison has a capacity of up to 1,640 inmates.
另根据巴西军警发布的最新数据显示，当天下午，共有3所监狱同时发生越狱事件，逃亡人数分别为400人、926人及30人，共计1356人。
According to the latest data released by the Brazilian military police, there were three simultaneous prison escapes in the afternoon, involving 400, 926 and 30 escapees, for a total of 1,356.
自当地时间本月12日起，为防止新冠肺炎疫情蔓延到监狱，巴西监狱系统实施了一系列限制人员出入及流动的新规。
Since December 12, local time, Brazil's prison system has implemented a series of new rules restricting the entry, exit and movement of people to prevent the outbreak from spreading to prisons.
当地时间16日，圣保罗法院决定在疫情期间暂时取消非紧急的审讯。
On the 16th day of local time, the Sao Paulo court decided to suspend non-urgent hearings during the outbreak.
自2月底巴西出现首个确诊病例，短短半月内，新冠肺炎疫情开始在拉美地区逐渐蔓延。
Brazil's first confirmed case began in late February, and in just over half a month, the outbreak began to spread in Latin America.
巴西卫生部官员在例行发布会上宣布，截至当地时间16日16时，全国确诊新冠肺炎病例234例，比前一天增长34例，疑似病例2064例。
As of 1600 hours local time, 234 new cases of pneumonia had been confirmed nationwide, an increase of 34 cases and a suspected 2,064 cases, officials from the Brazilian Ministry of Health said at a regular news conference.
截至目前，上周随巴西总统博索纳罗访美的团队中，已有13人新冠病毒检测呈阳性。
So far last week, 13 members of the Brazilian team that visited the United States have tested positive for the virus.
其中一人是巴西国家工业联合会主席罗布森·布拉加·德·安德拉德。
One of them was Robson Braga de Andrade, President of the National Confederation of Industry of Brazil.
据巴西媒体报道此人并没有乘坐总统博索纳罗的专机，而是在迈阿密的活动中会见了总统和其他官员。
According to Brazilian media reports, the man did not fly in President Basorro's plane, but met with the president and other officials at events in Miami.
另一人是巴西经济部外贸和国际事务特别秘书马科斯·特洛伊乔，他们均未出现任何症状，目前在家自我隔离。
The other is Marcos Troijo, Special Secretary for Foreign Trade and International Affairs of the Ministry of Economy of Brazil, who have no symptoms and are currently isolated at home.
位于巴西北部的亚马孙州宣布进入长达120天的公共卫生紧急状态，该州州长要求卫生系统的工作人员停止休假并返回工作岗位。
In the northwestern Brazilian state of Amazonia, where a 120-day public health emergency was declared, the governor asked health system workers to stop taking leave and return to work.
里约热内卢州州长威尔逊·维泽尔于当地时间16日宣布里约热内卢州进入紧急状态。
Rio de Janeiro Governor Wilson Weisel declared a state of emergency on the 16th local time.
由于全球新冠疫情不断升级，16日，巴西圣保罗股指（IBOVESPA）开盘后暴跌12%，随即触发熔断，这是两周来巴西股市第5次触发熔断机制。
Brazil's Sao Paulo stock index plunged 12% after opening trading yesterday, triggering a meltdown that marked the fifth time in two weeks that Brazil's stock market had triggered a meltdown.
此外，巴西足协15日决定，从16日起巴西国内所有全国性足球比赛将无限期暂停。
In addition, the Brazilian Football Association decided on the 15th, Brazil from 16 all national football matches will be suspended indefinitely.
美国多地考虑释放部分囚犯监狱里人员密集，环境封闭，活动空间有限，利于病毒传播，因此是各国重点关注对象。
The United States has focused its attention on the release of some of the prisoners, which are densely populated, enclosed and have limited space for the spread of the virus.
16日，据央视新闻援引英国媒体报道，英国监狱官员协会秘书长吉蓝（Gillan）表示，目前英国监狱系统已经有113名职员和75名服刑犯因出现疑似新冠病毒症状正在进行隔离，不过尚未有人确诊。
Gillan, secretary-general of the Association of Prison Officials, said 113 staff and 75 inmates were being quarantined for signs of a suspected new crown virus, but no one had yet confirmed it, CCTV News quoted British media as saying.
他说，目前英国还没有因疫情而提前释放关押犯人的计划，但是不排除这种可能。
He said there were no plans to release prisoners early because of the outbreak, but did not rule out the possibility.
此前，为控制疫情，监狱暂停家属探视的政策引发囚犯不满，意大利多所监狱发生骚乱。
Previously, the suspension of family visits in prisons to control the epidemic had led to discontent among prisoners and riots in several Italian prisons.
在3月8日至9日期间，至少50名囚犯在意大利全国27个监狱骚乱中逃脱。
Between 8 and 9 March, at least 50 prisoners escaped from riots in 27 prisons across Italy.
图片来源：看看新闻视频截图而美国多额地方正考虑释放部分囚犯。
Source: See the news video screenshot and many parts of the United States are considering releasing some prisoners.
美国加州当地时间3月16日，洛杉矶县警局局长埃里克斯在新闻发布会上表示，虽然目前在警员和囚犯中没有确诊的新冠肺炎病例，但为防止疫情的传播，洛杉矶县警局还是采取了包括减少监狱囚犯等措施。
Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department said at a news conference that although there are no confirmed new cases of pneumonia among police officers and prisoners, the Los Angeles County Police Department has taken steps to prevent the spread of the disease, including reducing prison inmates.
埃里克斯同时提醒民众，由于部分囚犯被提前释放，在防疫的同时，也要注意防范犯罪。
He also warned people to guard against crime as part of their early release from prison.
洛杉矶县警局局长埃里克斯埃里克斯还表示，洛杉矶县在过去一周内将逮捕人数从每天约300人减少到60人。
Los Angeles County Sheriff's Eric Eriksson also said Los Angeles County had reduced the number of arrests from about 300 to 60 a day in the past week.
警局正在通过提前释放囚犯等方法减少监狱人口，目前囚犯人数减少了约3.6%。
The police are in the process of reducing the prison population, including through the early release of prisoners, which has now been reduced by approximately 3.6 per cent.
目前，洛杉矶县关押的囚犯有1.7万多人，截至2月28日已经释放出600人，估计陆续还会释放更多犯人。
Los Angeles County currently holds more than 17,000 prisoners, and as of February 28, 600 have been released, with further releases expected.
据海外网报道，由于担心新冠病毒在监狱内传播开来，俄亥俄州凯霍加县的法官在上周末举行了特别听证会，试图通过达成认罪协议解决悬而未决的案件、释放囚犯、将他们软禁在家或是送回监狱。
Judges in Ohio held a special hearing at the weekend to try to resolve pending cases, release prisoners, place them under house arrest or return them to prison, fearing the spread of the virus within the prison, reports overseas.
凯霍加县司法中心（谷歌地图）根据统计数字，凯霍加县司法中心在上周共关押有近1900名囚犯。
Kaihoga County Judicial Center (Google Maps) According to statistics, the Kehoga County Judicial Center housed nearly 1,900 prisoners last week.
有美媒表示，在周末的听证会之后，预计将有200到300名囚犯获释，他们都是低级别罪犯。
American media said between 200 and 300 prisoners, all low-level criminals, are expected to be released after the weekend's hearings.
疫情严重的伊朗也在释放囚犯。
Iran, where the epidemic is severe, is also releasing prisoners.
3月9日，受新冠肺炎疫情影响，伊朗司法总监易卜拉欣·莱西表示，已经批准70000名符合条件的囚犯获得暂时释放。
On March 9, the head of the Iranian judiciary, Ibrahim Lacy, said 70,000 eligible prisoners had been granted provisional release following the outbreak of pneumonia in the New Crown.
他表示，患有潜在疾病的囚犯将优先获释。
He indicated that prisoners with potential illnesses would be released on a priority basis.
不容忽视的一点是，无论是囚犯被越来越多地释放，还是逮捕人数的减少，在疫情防控期间都将增加社会公共安全的风险。
It cannot be ignored that either the increasing release of prisoners or the decrease in arrests will increase the risk to public safety in society during the prevention and control of the epidemic.
